---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="Stokvel Society" description="Fintech platform for trust-based member contributions and payouts.">
  <div class="hand-drawn-frame p-8 space-y-8">
    <header class="space-y-4">
      <h1 class="hand-drawn-heading text-3xl">Stokvel Society</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-mid">A fintech platform for community savings and payouts, built with a trust-layer ledger that keeps member contributions accurate, auditable, and ready for distribution.</p>
    </header>

    <section class="grid lg:grid-cols-[1.4fr_1fr] gap-8 items-start">
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="hand-drawn-figure p-6">
          <h2 class="hand-drawn-heading text-2xl mb-4">Hero flow</h2>
          <svg class="hero-illustration w-full h-auto" viewBox="0 0 700 380" aria-hidden="true">
            <defs>
              <filter id="sketch" x="-10%" y="-10%" width="120%" height="120%">
                <feTurbulence type="fractalNoise" baseFrequency="0.02" numOctaves="2" result="noise" />
                <feDisplacementMap in="SourceGraphic" in2="noise" scale="2" />
              </filter>
            </defs>
            <rect x="40" y="60" width="180" height="120" rx="24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-dasharray="8 8" filter="url(#sketch)"/>
            <text x="130" y="95" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif" font-size="18" fill="currentColor">Member</text>
            <text x="130" y="120" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif" font-size="14" fill="currentColor">Contributions</text>

            <rect x="260" y="200" width="180" height="120" rx="24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-dasharray="8 8" filter="url(#sketch)"/>
            <text x="350" y="235" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif" font-size="18" fill="currentColor">Trust</text>
            <text x="350" y="260" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif" font-size="14" fill="currentColor">Ledger</text>

            <rect x="520" y="60" width="140" height="120" rx="24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-dasharray="8 8" filter="url(#sketch)"/>
            <text x="590" y="95" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif" font-size="18" fill="currentColor">Payouts</text>
            <text x="590" y="120" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif" font-size="14" fill="currentColor">Distribution</text>

            <path d="M 160 180 C 210 180 240 190 265 200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-dasharray="6 6" />
            <path d="M 445 200 C 495 200 525 180 555 160" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-dasharray="6 6" />
            <path d="M 600 100 C 470 130 390 145 350 145" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-dasharray="6 6" />
          </svg>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-mid mt-4">Illustrated flow from member contributions to ledger validation and payout distribution.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="hand-drawn-heading text-2xl">Why it matters</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-mid">Stokvel Society is designed for community trust. The platform records commitments clearly, keeps audit trails visible, and makes payouts predictable rather than manual.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="hand-drawn-card">
          <h3 class="font-mono text-xl mb-3">Key strengths</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-3 text-gray-mid">
            <li>Trusted ledger for member savings and payouts</li>
            <li>Transparent contribution tracking across each cycle</li>
            <li>Reliable distribution logic for payouts and audits</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="hand-drawn-card">
          <h3 class="font-mono text-xl mb-3">Fit for</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-mid">Community finance platforms, trust-based savings systems, and fintech products where correctness and clarity are essential.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
